Detailed Description

Exposes methods for enumerating a INktExportedFunctionsEnum collection.

Member Function Documentation

HRESULT INktExportedFunctionsEnum::_NewEnum ( [out, retval] IUnknown **  ppUnk)
get

Retrieves an enumerable collection object.

Parameters
[out,retval]ppUnk Address of an interface pointer that on return points to the IUnknown interface of an enumerator object.
Returns
S_OK on success,
E_POINTER if ppUnk is NULL.
E_FAIL on general failure.

Find an exported function by the given address.
